name: Erks Portal
description:
/“Let yourself explore the future
hand in hand with your very own heart
Keep an eye on your final figure 
And make yourself worthy of their Mysteries”

"Permítete explorar el futuro
de la mano de tu propio corazón.
Observa atentamente tu figura final
y hazte merecedor de sus Misterios."

Marcelo G. Martorelli
Extracto de "El llamado Planetario"/

Visual exploration of the stories that place certain Templar groups in relation with Erks, province of Cordoba.
